Name:                mkbndl
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.2
Version:             0.2.1
Synopsis:            Makes an OS X .app bundle from a binary.
Description:         Allows you to easily construct a .app bundle from a binary
                     complete with icon files and finder version info.
License:             GPL
License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Thomas Davie
Maintainer:          Thomas Davie (tom.davie@gmail.com)
Data-Files:          README
Category:            Distribution
build-type:          Simple

Executable mkbndl
  Build-Depends:        base >= 3.0,haskell98 >= 1.0,
                        filepath >= 1.1,directory >= 1.0
  Main-is:              Main.hs
  Other-Modules:        MakeBundle
